  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion criteria:

          -  Type 1 or type 2 diabetes

          -  Diabetic macular edema

        Exclusion criteria:

          -  Recent intra-ocular surgery in the study eye (e.g., cataract surgery in the last 6
             months)

          -  Recent laser photocoagulation in the study eye

          -  Recent treatment with Avastin, Lucentis, or intravitreal corticosteroids in the study
             eye

        Other protocol-defined inclusion/exclusion criteria applied
      </textblock>
